thread.title: Terri Nickell
thread.title_full: My Passport Photos reviewed by Terri Nickell

author: Terri Nickell
title: Terri Nickell
text: I did some searching for places to get my passport photos done--I needed 8 copies for visas and every place I looked where charging an over the top amount. With My Passport Photos I got 12 excellent quality photos from a picture taken on my I phone for the price the other's were charging me for 6 pictures. Great job, fast service--I would recommend them across the board as being quality, quantity and fast service!
